New Tab, New Window Reloaded
============================

This is an independent TypeScript reimplementation. The underlying idea —
opening every new tab in its own window via the Chrome extension APIs —
was popularized by "New Tab, New Window" by Ozawa Masayuki
<ozawa@coroq.com>, which is gratefully acknowledged here.

The source code, icon artwork, configuration features, and build tooling
in this project are original work, copyright (c) 2026 codellyson.

This acknowledgement is provided as a courtesy credit to the original
concept; it is not a claim that any code from the original project is
included here.
